    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "Following review of all 13 credibility factors and the multi-source provenance chain — including the cross-study literature synthesis node consolidating 14 prior validation campaigns — the assessment team determined that the weight of evidence supports acceptance for the intended COU. The literature synthesis provides integrative grounding for the Monte Carlo coefficient priors, and the primary bench validation demonstrates adequate agreement at three of five operating points. Remaining gaps are acknowledged and accepted under the current regulatory submission strategy.",
